August 03, 2017 11:10 AM ET
Textiles, Apparel and Luxury Goods

Company Overview of Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd manufactures, processes, and markets fine wool textile products, clothing products, and accessories in China, South Korea, the United States, and Japan. It offers dress and casual suits, short and long sleeve shirts, trousers, casual pants, T-shirts, jackets, sweaters, coats, cotton and leather products, and short sleeves products for men; and business attires, short and long shirts, suits, skirts, and pants for women. The company is based in Huangshi, China.


Industrial ParkDevelopment ZoneHuangshi,  435000China3,216 Employees



www.mailyard.com.cn







Key Executives for Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd


Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd does not have any Key Executives recorded. 



Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd Key Developments

Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd, Annual General Meeting, Jun 16, 2017
Apr 27 17
Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd, Annual General Meeting, Jun 16, 2017. Agenda: To discuss issues including the annual report of 2016 and its abstract; to discuss the scheme of profit distribution for 2016; and to discuss the proposal of renewing engagement of auditor for 2017.


Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd, Board Meeting, Apr 26, 2017
Apr 27 17
Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd, Board Meeting, Apr 26, 2017. Agenda: To approve the annual report of 2016 and its abstract; to discuss the scheme of profit distribution for 2016; and to discuss the full text and text of the 1st quarter report of 2017.


Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd. Reports Earnings Results for the First Quarter of 2017
Apr 27 17
Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd. reported earnings results for the first quarter of 2017. For the quarter, the company reported basic loss per share of CNY 0.014 and negative weighted average return on net assets of 0.91%.


