Hubei Mailyard Share Co Ltd Company Profile

IndustryApparel/Accessories
SectorConsumer Cyclical
Employees3216
Equity TypeORD


HUBEI MAILYARD SHARE CO.,LTD is principally engaged in the research, development, design, manufacture and distribution of apparel. The Company primarily provides apparel for women and men. The Company is also engaged in the operation of hotels, the futures business and real estate property business. The Company distributes its products in the domestic market and to overseas markets. 


