Summary for Hubei Mailyard Share Co.,Ltd.
Hubei Mailyard Share Co., Ltd is principally engaged in the development, design, manufacture and distribution of apparels, trappings and textile products. The Company is also engaged in the operation of hotels, as well as the leasing of properties. The Company distributes its products in the domestic market and to overseas markets. The Company operates its businesses in domestic and overseas markets. As of December 31, 2010, the Company had four major subsidiaries and one associate, which involved in the production of suits, dressings and evening dressings, restaurant and hotel services, as well as futures brokerage, among others.


