Description


Style Number:  MLY10-W211
Located Huangshi city, Hubei Province,by the Yangtze River, Hubei Mailyard Group Cooperation was founded in 1985 and has grown to be one of the largest textile and garment production and export basses in China. Since 1995,it has been enlisted as one Top Ten Enterprises of Textile Industry by State Statistics Bureau of China for consecutive years, and in 1996 was appointed as one of the 520 key enterprises in China. In 1997 Mailyard A was put into the Shanghai Stock Market. In 1998 its worsted fabric and men’s suit factories passed ISO9002 international quality system authentication. The Mailyard group owns an original value of fixed assets of RMB800million, and total assets of RMB2.4billion, with 20 subsidiary companies and 6 factories for garments production, the Group has some 8000 employees, with more than 8000pcs/sets of advanced machines of CAD/CAM pattern marking ,cutting, sewing, stitching, pressing and needle inspection imported from France, Japan, Italy, Germany, etc, we annually produce 1 million sets/pcs of high-quality men’s suit 200 thousand pcs of men’s coats, jackets, 3.2 million sets/pcs of various first-class ladies’ suits, ladies’ ensemble, ladies dress, shirts, blouses, jeans, 2 million meters of wool worsted fabric and 21 million meters good quality micro fiber fabric. Hubei Mailyard I/E Trade Company is s professional trade company and the sole agent on behalf of Mailyard Group in import and export business, our major business is saleing and promotion of the ladies’ garments, and now are developing to Germany, Finland, France, Spain, Japan, Italy, and H.K. SPD. An annual output is over USD120million.



