Company Description                    




                        The Company was established as a joint stock limited companyin 1993.  The  promoters to the establishment of the Companyare Huangsh Meierya Garment Head Plant ,  Huangsh  OutskirtsCountryside Credit Cooperative ,  Construction Bank of ChinaHubei  Trust  &  Investment Co .,  China  Bank Hubei Trust &Investment  Co.  and  Huangsh Electric Power Industrial HeadOffice.  With  the  approval  of China Securities RegulatoryCommission , the Company's  A shares were listed on SganghaiStock Exchange on Nov. 6 , 1997. It is a textile and garment enterprise specialized in foreign trade, mainly engaged in the manufacturing, processing and marketing of fine wool textile products, garment and accessories. The main products are famous all over the world and have a high market share in Japan. Mailyard suit was named "China top ten brand-name clothing", "China top ten brand-name suits," and won the European Quality Award, In addition, the company holds 90% stake of Mailyard Futures Brokerage Co., Ltd and has the only four-star hotel concerning foreign affairs in Huangshi city, Cihu villa Hotel.                    


